How to run (quick)

# From repo root
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install fastapi uvicorn

# Start dashboard
uvicorn api.server:app --reload --port 8000

# Open in browser
# http://localhost:8000


